# Design system

Full reference: `DESIGN-SYSTEM.md`. **Reuse primitives before one-offs.**

## Scalability rules

1. **Data in `lib/*.ts`** — sections stay thin compositions.
2. **Server Components default** — `"use client"` only for interactivity (accordion, filters, carousel, form, header).
3. **Shared constants** — `layout-constants`, `heading-styles`, `surface-styles`, `section-backdrops`, `cta-styles`.
4. **Import from `@/components/ui`** barrel — extend inventory, don't duplicate.
5. **`next/image`** for all images; `priority` only on Hero LCP assets.

## Layout

- `LAYOUT_OUTER_CLASS` (1280px) + `LAYOUT_INNER_CLASS` (1216px rail)
- `py-section` / `mt-section` = 120px; partners gap after hero = `pt-10` (40px)
- Light sections: `<Section background="surface">`

## Backdrop presets (`lib/section-backdrops.ts`)

| Preset | Sections |
|--------|----------|
| `challenges` | Founder journey, Case studies, Founder-led studio, Final CTA |
| `investment` | Investment band, PreTRACTION newsletter, Eterna panel |
| `services` | Services, Solutions |

Investment band: `investmentTopBandClass` + `investmentTopBandFadeClass`.

## Surfaces

- Dark borders: `border-border-dark`
- Light borders: `border-border-muted`
- Guide/Blog gradient: `lightResourceGradientClasses` from `lib/surface-styles.ts`
  - 15+ stat (`StatCard variant="gradient"`), Build process step, gradient resource tiles, select reviews

## Icons

**Default: `text-brand-purple-light`.** Pink only via flags: Engine 02 `highlight`, Services `iconHighlight`, process `PhaseLabel highlight`.

## Typography

- Dark H2: `SectionHeading` — `displayHeadingTypeClasses`, `font-black`, `tracking-[-2px]`
- Hero / Final CTA: `text-display-lg sm:text-display-xl`, bold
- Light editorial: `LightEditorialDisplay` + `lightEditorialLineClasses` / `lightEditorialAccentLineClasses`

## CTAs (`lib/cta-styles.ts`)

- Dark primary: `CallToActionLink` (white pill)
- Dark secondary: `SecondaryCtaLink` (outlined)
- Light: `LightCtaLink` (black pill)
- Arrows: straight `ArrowUpRight`

## Light chapter patterns

- **Partners:** marquee only, no heading, `from-bg-surface` edge fades
- **Spread columns:** left `lg:sticky max-w-[400px]`, right `max-w-[480px]`
- **ProcessStepCard:** conditional `showTopBorder`; skip borders around `gradientBackground` step
- **AutoAccordion:** pass `items[]`, default 9s rotation

## Homepage order (14 + footer)

Hero → HomeLightChapter → FounderJourney → EternaSystem → Services → HomeApproachChapter → CaseStudies → Solutions → HomeClientStoriesChapter → FounderLedStudio → HomeResourcesChapter → Investment → Faq → FinalCta → Footer

## Footer

- `border-t border-white/10`
- Newsletter: `sectionBackdropPresets.investment`
- Links: `grid-cols-3 w-full` aligned to newsletter column
- ETERNA watermark: `absolute bottom-0`, `[clip-path:inset(0_0_40%_0)]`

## Data files

`founder-journey`, `eterna-engines`, `services`, `approach-callouts`, `tool-stack`, `process-steps`, `case-studies`, `solutions`, `partners`, `client-stories`, `founder-studio`, `resources`, `investment`, `faq`, `footer`

## New section checklist

1. `lib/<name>.ts` data + types
2. `components/sections/<Name>.tsx` using existing ui primitives
3. Pick backdrop preset or `Section` background
4. Add to page route
5. Update `DESIGN-SYSTEM.md` if new pattern
